my vimrc 
more details @http://lostjs.com/2012/02/04/use-pathogen-and-git-to-manage-vimfiles/
1 pathogen, @https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen
  plugin manager
  bundle/vim-pathogen

2 supertab, https://github.com/ervandew/supertab
  auto complete
  bundle/vim-supertab 

--------------
1 更新插件
  更新单个插件: git checkout master; git pull
  更新所有插件: git submodule foreach 'git checkout master && git pull'

2 删除插件
  rm -rf bundle/插件名
  git rm -r bundle/插件名

3 安装 
  git submodule add plugin_repository_in_git bundle/plugin_name
  样例――安装supertab: git submodule add git@github.com:ervandew/supertab.git bundle/vim_supertab

